      "text": "🚨 FRAUD UPDATE: Under the leadership of @VP and alongside @USLaborIG on the @WHFraudTF, we’re hunting down fraudsters and recovering taxpayer dollars.  \n\n➡️ $135 BILLION in unemployment benefits was stolen through COVID-era fraud.  \n\n➡️ @USDOL has frozen $520 MILLION tied to fraudulent activity.  \n\n➡️ We’re now tracking down another $912 MILLION sitting on prepaid debit cards.  \n\nLEARN MORE: https://t.co/RQUOeTg7Ni",
