      "text": "Under @POTUS’ leadership, @USDOL recovered roughly $4.3 billion in unspent and unused COVID funds and returned it to the Treasury.\n\nAs I serve on the @VP’s Task Force to Eliminate Fraud, we will continue restoring integrity in the Unemployment Insurance system, prevent fraud before it happens, and hold criminals accountable.",
